      "contentTypeKey": "5781df7b-a32c-4493-b9fc-90c8e9efebb2",
      "udi": "umb://element/cdaea65c817f48efb16e0c79a25c77f6",
      "negativePositive": "0",
      "lockInType": [
        "Economical"
      ],
      "bodyText": "<p>The push to persuade households to purchase zero emission vehicles (VEVs) has come at a price. The policy has contributed to a sizeable revenue decline from car-related excise duties. The tax expenditure from the VAT exemption reached NOK 11.3 billion (USD 1.3 billion) in 2021.</p>"
    }
